/*
 Beep
 
 Test different pre-configured beeps on
 the robot's speaker.

 Possible beeps are:
 - BEEP_SIMPLE
 - BEEP_DOUBLE
 - BEEP_LONG
 
 Circuit:
 * Arduino Robot
 
 created 1 May 2013
 by X. Yang
 modified 12 May 2013
